{"tid":1335494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會投注站7/21有4間全日暫停營業","createTime":"2019-07-20T14:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T14:18:06.000Z","uid":81783,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f07e3e06e00c496b1dc65f57daf0c3d57c06a2cd","tid":1335494,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港賽馬會四間場外投注處將於7月21日暫停服務 (灣仔軒尼詩道、謝斐道、春園街及中環天星碼頭)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4znh3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4znh3D.jpg&h=e51f278a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次上水同沙田,馬會都係預早一日通知關閉投注站<br />\n<br />\n即係代表灣仔入夜後會變成「極危險」之地<br />\n<br />\n警方可能會採取同上水&amp;沙田一樣既行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"94c35f4902861e6166066bb6468d3be1caecdd51","tid":1335494,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"我真係好撚驚呀"},{"pid":"9c6ac44a6ae0e1250b17e4f835bbf50c47d0f6c5","tid":1335494,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94c35f4902861e6166066bb6468d3be1caecdd51","tid":1335494,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"我真係好撚驚呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"各位注意安全啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}